" title="Omnibus Foreign Trade and Competitiveness Act">1988</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Canada-U.S._Free_Trade_Agreement" title="Canada-U.S. Free Trade Agreement" class="mw-redirect">1989: Canada FT</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/North_American_Free_Trade_Agreement" title="North American Free Trade Agreement">1993: NAFTA</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/World_Trade_Organization" title="World Trade Organization">1994: WTO</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/2002_United_States_steel_tariff" title="2002 United States steel tariff">2002: Steel</a></div>
